{"tid":155430,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中文oral 唔好死 oral checklist轉載","createTime":"2017-03-14T04:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T08:27:22.000Z","uid":68666,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94f26aea76e814626bb8e07da3227413c244f785","tid":155430,"uid":68666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:42:12.000Z","msg":"作為過來人<br />\n其實oral好易攞分㗎咋<br />\n因為好多垃圾考生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉載自 <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1810477375871638&amp;id=1466507586935287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1810477375871638%26id%3D1466507586935287&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3176a1e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1810477375871638&amp;id=1466507586935287</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知各位study leave成點呢? 聽日開始就係中文oral啦~<br />\n大家記得要早啲休息呀~記得study leave唔好溫書溫到凌晨先瞓，要keep住早睡早起，唔係到時DSE開始果陣一早起身就唔夠精神，影響埋考試狀態呀~<br />\n同埋提下大家記得去行一轉考場先(唔識果啲)，預返個路程同車程，費事遲到啦。<br />\n下面呢，就有一個關於中文oral嘅check list比大家睇睇，再下面就share返之前出過中文說話技巧分享啦~<br />\n<br />\n出門口前<br />\n( ) 帶準考證<br />\n( ) 帶身份證<br />\n( ) 帶原子筆<br />\n( ) 帶水<br />\n( ) 帶溫習材料 (無得用手機，要等) (可帶書)<br />\n( ) 帶褸<br />\n( ) 帶個腦<br />\n( ) 帶個自信嘅自己<br />\n( ) 預留足夠時間搵考場!<br />\n<br />\n去到考場<br />\n( ) 拎返輕鬆自信嘅自己出嚟<br />\n( ) 唔洗注意人地做咩<br />\n( ) 比個腦休息放鬆自己<br />\n<br />\n做題目個陣<br />\n( ) 記得記得: 自信!<br />\n( ) 搵題目關鍵詞出黎（至少一個）<br />\n( ) 幫助討論嘅定義，勿為講而講<br />\n( ) 明確並合適嘅準則<br />\n( ) 多角度思考（個人家庭社會/社會經濟文化...）<br />\n( ) 兼論<br />\n( ) 比較選項<br />\n( ) 唔好辯論，專注討論，留意溝通<br />\n( ) 勿壟斷<br />\n( ) 記得解釋例子<br />\n( ) 用下個腦<br />\n( ) 記得要回應/總結下立場論點<br />\n( ) 比較/優次題唔好貶低其他option"},{"pid":"b5d2fdb2d802a09316701495da740cd52b78c8e4","tid":155430,"uid":54973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"17號考啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3e0907f01b1ff6d1a205dce6f2fefd3f627fe5","tid":155430,"uid":24200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"23號考<br />\n最尾嗰日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccec0427dfab33d36658c42c3452f7ae6598a01c","tid":155430,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"聽日考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950f3a387985b75807642a59f4fc73536cce88fc","tid":155430,"uid":5844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"好在係21號啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdfcaebcf0531523b5681b42fc65812411fb6d6","tid":155430,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好在係21號啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1"},{"pid":"01597fc528da26f6cf8ade1d0dbf6ec71827aca3","tid":155430,"uid":20928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"今日五點考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全港第一批玩大屠殺"},{"pid":"4b8e652a3f54b0ff425e4873321fece2d34ad10e","tid":155430,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:01:25.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒左去科大跳蘑菇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb886be6274086423f0a185026398794e0672926","tid":155430,"uid":61467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"陣間6點半考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a033debd0b69e593c08131b32fcad18ec2f50ab8","tid":155430,"uid":26037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"頭幾日考先好<br />\nd題目易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73269b167b4037c9e88389fe0706d22616f9432e","tid":155430,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"29e9e1e03227e28975c470257aae711c9615cb04","tid":155430,"uid":30901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:20:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭幾日考先好<br />\nd題目易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係同時壓力都好撚大<br />\n<br />\n陣間6點半考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6be963c54748c5bbd9f07bde66d3b999a0ab33","tid":155430,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>23號考<br />\n最尾嗰日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我當年中英都係最尾一日考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我試過問一問佢遇到嘅考生大概係點<br />\n佢可以滿足告解嘅需要之餘自己又可以心中有數<br />\n<br />\n畢竟會練oral嘅人唔會有唔正常嘅人，好合理姐"},{"pid":"e6a5c557e63fb0bb5fa522f9f29a975cbb716f80","tid":155430,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99810c2133341980cdd6a7576a149c83c5a69480","tid":155430,"uid":54973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頭幾日考先好<br />\nd題目易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係同時壓力都好撚大<br />\n<br />\n陣間6點半考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都冇分難易架啦<br />\n上年第一日已經象徵題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw加油巴打"},{"pid":"997f854794e1ca3c93e6570fb879da3be4a1514c","tid":155430,"uid":78703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:27:22.000Z","msg":"唔係基道中學考就收皮啦"}]}